item.title: [HIVE-21938] Add database and table filter options to PreUpgradeTool
item.description:
By default pre upgrade tool scans all databases and tables in the warehouse.
Add database and table filter options to run the tool for a specific subset of databases and tables only.
item.summary: Add database and table filter options to PreUpgradeTool

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
